s://github.com/feketemihai\n    ```\n  maintainer-mcojocaru: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/mcojocaru.png?size=40px\n    :alt: mcojocaru\n    :target: https://github.com/mcojocaru\n    ```\n---\n\n# Romania - Stock Accounting Notice\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:590c1364f71578d94f720bd4ea788f10bc5eb12ecb8d622b98a522a3fe2564f8\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThe module is managing price diferences between invoices and receptions.\nIt will create a landed cost with a \"Price Difference\" product available\nin the configuration.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-romania/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-romania/issues/new?body=module:%20l10n_ro_stock_account_notice%0Aversion:%2018.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- NextERP Romania\n- Dorin Hongu\n\n### Contributors\n\n- [NextERP Romania](https://www.nexterp.ro):\n\n  - Fekete Mihai \\<<mailto:feketemihai@nexterp.ro>>\n  - Cojocaru Marcel \\<<mailto:cojocarumarcel@nexterp.ro>>\n\n- [Terrabit](https://www.terrabit.ro):\n\n  - Dorin Hongu \\<<mailto:dhongu@gmail.com>>\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with\ntechnical issues.\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nCurrent [maintainers](https://odoo-community.org/page/maintainer-role):\n\n{{ maintainer-feketemihai }} {{ maintainer-mcojocaru }} {{ maintainer-dhongu }}\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/l10n-romania](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-romania/tree/18.0/l10n_ro_stock_account_notice) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_stock_account_notice.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_stock_account_notice.models.account_move", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_stock_account_notice.models..account_move", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_stock_account_notice.models.account_move_line", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_stock_account_notice.models..account_move_line", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_stock_account_notice.models.product", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_stock_account_notice.models..product", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_stock_account_notice.models.purchase_order", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_stock_account_notice.models..purchase_order", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_stock_account_notice.models.stock_move", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_stock_account_notice.models..stock_move", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_stock_account_notice.models.stock_picking", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_stock_account_notice.models..stock_picking", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_stock_account_notice.models.account_move_line", "documentat